name: QuakeReport
0:
”Alexa, open Quake Report.”
”Alexa, ask Quake Report for earthquakes last hour.”
”Alexa, ask Quake Report for earthquakes previous week.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: quake report
des: Want to know whether an earthquake occurred last hour or yesterday? Quake report can get you real-time reports even for the past week. And the data is updated every 5 minutes, so you won't miss one.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
